  "2026-07-10T16:57:36.687Z",maintainer-agent,"Root-cause narrowing (review 2026-07-10, current main build): the GH-489 repro still fails — fresh workspace with one status=blocked item yields summary.blocked: 0 AND candidates: 1, i.e. the status=blocked item is excluded from the candidate pool entirely, not merely miscounted. Contrast: the real workspace reports blocked: 25 with zero status=blocked items (pm stats), so next's blocked counter is derived from open items with open blockers (graph-blocked). Fix likely needs BOTH paths: include status=blocked items in candidates/summary and populate the companion from the union of status-blocked + graph-blocked. Regression test should assert candidates counts them too."
